      "description": "Priced to move, this vehicle offers an affordable entry point for a handy buyer, commuter backup, or project opportunity. It shows age and wear consistent with its condition, but still presents solid value for someone looking for low-cost transportation or a platform to improve over time. Straightforward, budget-friendly, and backed by a transparent listing from a trusted seller.",
