    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left in it? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable transportation without spending a fortune. It\u2019s a great fit for a daily runaround, first car, or project for someone who enjoys giving a vehicle a little TLC. Priced fairly and represented honestly by a seller who believes in being upfront and easy to deal with.",
