      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Tough, honest driver with solid old-school character and plenty of usable life left for the right buyer. Starts, runs, and moves under its own power, making it a strong candidate for a budget commuter, winter beater, or light project build. Powertrain feels straightforward and serviceable, with the kind of mechanical simplicity DIY owners appreciate. Cosmetic wear and age-related flaws are present, but that\u2019s reflected in the price. If you want an inexpensive car with decent utility and a good foundation for cleanup or continued daily use, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 6900.0,
