      "description": "Here\u2019s a car with honest character and plenty of story left to write. It\u2019s the kind of ride that appeals to someone who sees potential, appreciates a no-nonsense daily driver, or wants a solid starting point for a hands-on project. With a presence that still turns heads in the right light and a price that makes room for your own vision, this is an opportunity to get behind the wheel without stretching the budget. If you\u2019ve been looking for inexpensive transportation with personality, this one deserves a look.",
